title: Gautam Govinda
subTitle: Gautam, a dedicated officer, is transferred to a town that is teeming with criminals and ruled by Dharamdutt. In order to tackle Gautam, Dharamdutt sends his most able and trusted man, Govinda.

title: Kunwara Baap
subTitle: A rickshaw driver's life changes when he finds an abandoned baby at his doorstep. When the child is affected by polio, he has a change of heart and decides to care for him.

title: Saaransh
subTitle: When Pradhan and Parvati lose their son, they open their home to Sujata Suman, a struggling actress. Her presence brings comfort and renewed hope to the mourning parents.

title: Bahurani
subTitle: Amit wants to marry a modern woman but his parents get him married to a village girl, Madhuri. When Amit refuses to accept her as his wife, Madhuri reinvents herself as Malathi and re-enters his life.

title: Sitara
subTitle: The life of a couple who shifts to Mumbai to prepare for their marriage, undergoes a drastic change when the lady becomes a popular movie star overnight and forgets her purpose amidst the glamour.

title: Jheel Ke Us Paar
subTitle: Sameer falls in love with Neelu, a girl with visual impairment, and plans to restore her sight. However, his mother disapproves of their union and hatches a plot to break them apart.

title: Kuchhe Dhaage
subTitle: To avenge his father's death, Lakhan kills Roopa's father, Tulsiram, in cold blood. Enraged, Roopa decides to kill him, but fate has its own plans.

title: Do Chor
subTitle: Tony, a burglar, comes under the radar of suspicion when a series of mysterious thefts bewilder the police. Soon enough, he tries to redeem his honour by going after the real criminal.

title: Dacait
subTitle: After being mercilessly beaten and abandoned to die, a young man is rescued by a band of dacoits, who nurse him back to health in their hidden lair.

title: Dosti Dushmani
subTitle: Sandeep, Ranjit and Prakash are best friends from childhood. A misunderstanding between Ranjit and Sandeep leads the former to believe that the latter is a criminal.

title: Dosti Dushmani
subTitle: Sandeep, Ranjit and Prakash are best friends from childhood. A misunderstanding between Ranjit and Sandeep leads the former to believe that the latter is a criminal.

title: Anamika
subTitle: A writer rescues an injured woman who suffers from memory loss but claims to be his wife. In the process of finding out her real identity, he falls in love with her.

title: Amir Garib
subTitle: Mohanlal, a musician and a thief, robs rich people and distributes the money amongst the poor. However, things take a turn when he falls for Sunita, a wealthy man's daughter.

title: Dastaan-E-Rafi
subTitle: Renowned celebrities discuss the life journey of gifted singer Mohammed Rafi, sharing moments and incidents they experienced with him during his career.

title: Khoon Ki Pukaar
subTitle: A compassionate pujari, Vidya, shelters a maimed bandit, unaware of his hidden motives. Subsequently, Vidya must confront a moral dilemma that could change their lives forever.

title: Kanyadaan
subTitle: Rekha and Amar are married off in their childhood. Years later, Rekha learns about Amar's wedding to Lata and Kumar's real identity.

title: Mera Naam Joker
subTitle: Raju faces many hurdles and disappointments in matters of the heart throughout his life. But as a clown in a circus, he tries to make his audience laugh at the cost of his own sorrows.

title: Adalat
subTitle: Dharma leaves his village and moves to Mumbai to lead a better life. However, things take an ugly turn when the police suspects his connection in a criminal case and arrests him.

title: Mard
subTitle: Azad, a wealthy prosperous king, is locked in a dungeon by General Dyer who wants to take over his kingdom. Years later, Azad's son comes to his father's rescue and puts an end to Dyer's tyranny.

title: Mard Ki Zabaan
subTitle: The lives of brothers Ram and Lakshman are irrevocably changed when Ram marries Raghupati's daughter, triggering a series of events that lead to loss and lamentation.

title: Mard Ki Zabaan
subTitle: The lives of brothers Ram and Lakshman are irrevocably changed when Ram marries Raghupati's daughter, triggering a series of events that lead to loss and lamentation.

title: Shehzada
subTitle: Bantu, a middle-class man, grows up being neglected by his cold-hearted father, Valmiki. However, his world is shaken when he learns that he was switched at birth.

title: Abhinetri
subTitle: Stage artist Anjana takes a break from her career after marrying the love of her life, Shekhar. As time passes, their individual expectations start to clash and put a strain on their relationship.

title: Love in Tokyo
subTitle: While in Japan to pick up his orphaned nephew, Ashok becomes locked in a romantic misadventure with Asha, a troubled woman who is a master of disguises.

title: Lav Kush
subTitle: After Ram returns to Ayodhya, Sita is forced to go into exile. She gives birth to twins Lav and Kush, who later go to Ayodhya to attain blessings of Ram and recite the Ramayan.

title: Kudrat Ka Kanoon
subTitle: When the good doctor Vijay is falsely accused and imprisoned, his wife and daughter, desperately seeking justice, are terrorised and slandered by the harsh eyes of the society.

title: Mehboob Ki Mehndi
subTitle: Shabana is employed by Yusuf, a rich man, to teach his nephew. Eventually, Yusuf and Shabana fall in love and plan to get married. But the girl has a troubled past that may destroy her future.

title: Karz
subTitle: Monty discovers the shocking truth about his past life when he was killed by his gold-digger wife, while his family was rendered homeless. Supported by his lover, he decides to set things right.

title: Kasam Suhaag Ki
subTitle: Troubles arise for Surajmukhi after her husband, Sultan, is gunned down and she and her daughter get abducted by goons. She tries her best to get revenge and escape with her child.
